OL,3,CTrump says he cancelled imminent
OL,4,Cstrike on Iran after Gulf ally request
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump said he is
OL,7,Fholding off on a military strike on
OL,8,FIran planned for Tuesday after Gulf
OL,9,Fallies requested a delay due to
OL,10,F"serious negotiations" being underway.
OL,12,FTrump's announcement in a social media
OL,13,Fpost Monday came as he had threatened
OL,14,Fthat the clock was ticking for Iran to
OL,15,Fstrike a deal or fighting would renew
OL,16,Fafter a fragile ceasefire.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
