OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779152635
OL,3,CTrump says he cancelled imminent
OL,4,Cstrike on Iran after Gulf ally request
OL,6,FThe president did not offer details
OL,7,Fabout the planned attack but said he
OL,8,Finstructed the US military "to be
OL,9,Fprepared to go forward with a full,
OL,10,Flarge scale assault of Iran, on a
OL,11,Fmoment's notice, in the event that an
OL,12,Facceptable Deal is not reached."
OL,14,FTrump had not previously disclosed
OL,15,Fthat he was planning a strike for May
OL,16,F19, but over the weekend, he warned,
OL,17,F"For Iran, the Clock is Ticking, and
OL,18,Fthey better get moving, FAST, or there
OL,19,Fwon't be anything left of them."
OL,26,@pD@\OUtD@`O]yD@AOU{D@`O]
