OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779152635
OL,3,CTrump says he cancelled imminent
OL,4,Cstrike on Iran after Gulf ally request
OL,6,FTrump has been threatening for weeks
OL,7,Fthat the ceasefire struck in mid-April
OL,8,Fcould end if Iran did not strike a
OL,9,Fdeal, with shifting parameters for
OL,10,Fstriking such an agreement.
OL,12,FTrump said in his social media post
OL,13,Fthat he was calling off the planned
OL,14,Fstrike at the request of allies in the
OL,15,FMiddle East, including the leaders of
OL,16,FQatar, Saudi Arabia and the United
OL,17,FArab Emirates.
OL,19,FTrump has repeatedly set deadlines for
OL,20,FTehran and then backed off.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
