OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779152635
OL,3,CTrump says he cancelled imminent
OL,4,Cstrike on Iran after Gulf ally request
OL,6,FThe US president in recent days has
OL,7,Falso spoken with Israeli Prime
OL,8,FMinister Benjamin Netanyahu and
OL,9,FChinese President Xi Jinping about the
OL,10,FIran war.
OL,12,FAlthough the war has technically been
OL,13,Fpaused for a ceasefire for weeks, the
OL,14,FUS and Iran have still traded blows.
OL,16,FThe US has blockaded all of Iran's
OL,17,Fports and detained several Iranian-
OL,18,Fflagged vessels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
