OL,3,CTrump says he cancelled imminent
OL,4,Cstrike on Iran after Gulf ally request
OL,6,FA drone struck an electricity
OL,7,Fgenerator outside the inner perimeter
OL,8,Fof Barakah Nuclear Power Plant, in the
OL,9,FUnited Arab Emirates, on Sunday,
OL,10,Fsparking a fire on the site.
OL,12,FNo one immediately claimed
OL,13,Fresponsibility for the strike, which
OL,14,Fthe UAE foreign ministry described as
OL,15,Fan "unprovoked terrorist attack" in a
OL,16,Fstatement.
OL,18,FThe plant was built by the UAE with
OL,19,Fthe help of South Korea, and is the
OL,20,Fonly nuclear power plant in the Arab
OL,21,Fworld.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
